      <tr><td>DataSource</td><td>object</td><td>N/A</td><td>Determines the data source that will be loaded to the group panel.<br />Each member of the <strong>dataSource</strong> array is an object with the following fields:<ul><li><strong>dataField</strong> - the dataField of the column to be grouped.</li><li><strong>dataType</strong> - the data type of the column to be grouped.</li><li><strong>groupIndex</strong> - the group order of columns. If this value is -1, the grouping will not be applied by this column initially.</li><li><strong>label</strong> - the column label to be displayed in the column selection input.</li><li><strong>icon</strong> - a specific class to be applied to the respective item in the column selection input.</li><li><strong>sortDirection</strong> - the sort direction to be applied when grouping. Possible values: <em>'ascending'</em> and <em>'descending'</em>.</li></ul></td></tr>
